Title : Rosina Fernhoff
Text : '''Rosina Fernhoff''' (born April 13, 1931)<ref>[https://familysearch.org/pal:/MM9.1.1/KJFT-7N5 Date of birth], familysearch.org; accessed May 31, 2014.</ref> is an American actress known for her work in the theatre. She often performs plays that deal with [[Jewish philosophy|Jewish]] themes. 
{{Infobox person
